subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: After an eight-year hiatus, Kim Clijsters made a return to doubles at the Open, where she and a fellow Belgian, Kirsten Flipkens, lost to Chia-Jung Chuang and Zhang Shuai, 6-3, 6-4.
